{"tid":2364946,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天下雜誌調查　台灣信心創新高　大陸國台辦：錯誤道路必遭嚴懲","createTime":"2021-01-13T11:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T11:28:35.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4f09cad58e1890a456dd2a4b120cfdc87c45cc","tid":2364946,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/limszewah/posts/10160772448697571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flimszewah%2Fposts%2F10160772448697571&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEU8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=783e533f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/limszewah/posts/10160772448697571</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Simon Lim<br />\n<br />\n《天下雜誌》2021年國情調查：<br />\n國人對台灣的信心創下近 20年來新高；對台灣目前經濟表現滿意度創新高；對國家未來發展樂觀者達48.9％，同樣是新高點；對總統蔡英文滿意度維持去年高位，滿意者48.4％，高於不滿意者46.8％；不僅在領導人連任期間少見，甚至打破了前總統馬英九、陳水扁的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n大陸國台辦：<br />\n民進黨當局頑固「倚美謀獨」，在錯誤的道路上越走越遠，只會給台灣民眾帶來災難，必遭嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5106990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cw.com.tw%2Farticle%2F5106990&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEU8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=74e87db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5106990</a>"},{"pid":"4bc15de1166c9abc0987e6c76451a93d58f9fa4c","tid":2364946,"uid":357030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"對自己地頭有信心都要被人嚴懲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb8967da1e1e42f0347eff4563e80a039b1deae","tid":2364946,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"支那:好嬲好嬲 拉下香港人等你驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}